        {
          "content_hash": "7d4aaa4a12081b1c",
          "style": "NORMAL_TEXT",
          "text": "UIUC Heng Ji （？ji老师人很好啊）（存在争议，请谨慎辨别）"
        },
        {
          "content_hash": "e72fe2168bdc2579",
          "style": "NORMAL_TEXT",
          "text": "组里phd，去年刚毕业，overall Heng不算完美，但是也是在方方面面fully supportive。有时候比较严厉会批评做的不好的地方（对事不对人），其他时候相处融洽，来世还当heng学生（我也想去miromind!）"
        },
        {
          "content_hash": "64984375e3784d9a",
          "style": "NORMAL_TEXT",
          "text": "比较以funding project为重，早八晚零敬业型advisor，人很nice很容易相处"
        },
        {
          "content_hash": "abedce30ca2ee119",
          "style": "NORMAL_TEXT",
          "text": "老师组里三个track，near-future faculty 相当于 TBD，PHD student 属于 TBD collaborator，研究生和本科生属于 MSL"
        },
        {
          "content_hash": "cfa6bb5659495840",
          "style": "NORMAL_TEXT",
          "text": "Heng真的nice(+1) (+2)"
        },
        {
          "content_hash": "ec88db6c92d6d2b5",
          "style": "NORMAL_TEXT",
          "text": "上述请去红榜说。。。季姮就属于打听学生phd offer，一开始就是画饼，给一堆鱼offer，最后只挑把她列top1的。天生愿意给她当牛马肯定好处多多:)"
        },
        {
          "content_hash": "0000000000000000",
          "style": "NORMAL_TEXT",
          "text": ""
        },
        {
          "content_hash": "0000000000000000",
          "style": "NORMAL_TEXT",
          "text": ""
        },
        {
          "content_hash": "cc042550d57c523b",
          "style": "NORMAL_TEXT",
          "text": "UIUC Yu-Xiong Wang"
        },
        {
          "content_hash": "2eab565214af0c7c",
          "style": "NORMAL_TEXT",
          "text": "听说对学生比较push"
        },
        {
          "content_hash": "2e4d8de0cd60d72b",
          "style": "NORMAL_TEXT",
          "text": "听说不放学生毕业"
        },
        {
          "content_hash": "14accec82e5d52ab",
          "style": "NORMAL_TEXT",
          "text": "学生纯牛马，拿PhD当postdoc用，还都延毕"
        },
        {
          "content_hash": "4c9c4d0f38eb8916",
          "style": "NORMAL_TEXT",
          "text": "对学术比较push，不放学生毕业"
        },
        {
          "content_hash": "8cbc874360bec513",
          "style": "NORMAL_TEXT",
          "text": "听说有intern闹掰了"
        },
        {
          "content_hash": "af88f19a6d00cf19",
          "style": "NORMAL_TEXT",
          "text": "听说intern申请结果最好只有uiuc ms（有认识intern最后去了CMU LTI PhD）"
        },
        {
          "content_hash": "785ce9bca3ac9cdd",
          "style": "NORMAL_TEXT",
          "text": "听说对phd不是很好"
        },
